summary: Adds Milk and Butter to the Hearthfire Crafting Supply Chests.
descriptionHtml:
It always bothered me that my steward would work her ass off around the house mining ore, clay, stone, and crafting. Where did these materials go? I have a cow but no milk, a butter churn but no butter. This mod adds 10 milk & 10 butter to the crafting chest that re-spawns due the hard work of my steward. 

Hearthfire required.
author: whatnameisnotalreadyused
